item.title: Server: Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?
item.dc:creator: @Soul_Breaker Soul Breaker
item.description:
@Soul_Breaker wrote:

It would mean that your port is different, and you could probably use another runserver but a different kind of Server
For Example: Devolution and Project Czar.

If you use the same ones, it won’t work.

Note: if you want to change the port, go to server.java
search: 43594 replace it with 5555.

NOTE: But watch out! there might be some viruses or hackers in the port.
